#: ../../language/error_codes/E4176.md:1
msgid "E4176"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4176.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `invalid_lexmatch_target`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4176.md:5
msgid "Invalid `lexmatch` target."
msgstr "无效的 `lexmatch` 目标。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4176.md:7
msgid ""
"`lexmatch` works on textual views. The target expression must have a type"
" that can be matched by regex patterns, such as `String` or `StringView`,"
" instead of a numeric, boolean, or other unrelated type."
msgstr ""
"`lexmatch` 作用于文本视图。目标表达式的类型必须可以被正则模式匹配，例如 "
"`String` 或 `StringView`，而不能是数值、布尔值或其他无关类型。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4176.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4176.md:13
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn match_number(n : Int) -> Unit {\n"
"  lexmatch n with longest {\n"
"    _ => ()\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4176.md:17
msgid "The target is an `Int`, which cannot be consumed by `lexmatch`."
msgstr "目标是 `Int`，不能被 `lexmatch` 消费。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4176.md:19
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "修改建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4176.md:21
msgid "Match a string-like value, or convert the input before using `lexmatch`."
msgstr "匹配类似字符串的值，或者在使用 `lexmatch` 前先转换输入。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4176.md:23
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn match_text(text : String) -> Unit {\n"
"  lexmatch text with longest {\n"
"    _ => ()\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
